I am looking for a "calendar" style date selection element for templates. 

Our template design is to create a form the user fills out, automating (to some extent) the creation of wiki pages. It would be great to have a way to display a calendar users could select dates from, instead of our current solution, which is typing into a text box.

This would be nice because it would force consistency (the information's format would be generated) and ease of user interaction (a visual interface/cue instead of typing).

